ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 3rd day of November, 2015, the Motion Seeking Leave to Exceed Word Count Limit is DENIED, and Petitioner is DIRECTED to file a compliant Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 30 days.
